"{\"uid\": \"lbc.co.uk-article-eurostar-london-st-pancras-france-cancelled-olympics-train-arson-5HjcnmQ_2\", \"text\": \"By Flaminia Luck  A quarter of Eurostar services have been cancelled for the second day after vandals attacked France's high-speed rail lines.  Co-ordinated arson attacks on the day of the Olympics' opening ceremony have led to widespread disruption and travel chaos.  Engineers are still working to fix lines damaged in co-ordinated arson attacks.  Services between London and Paris have been hit with delays and cancellations.  However, the French rail operator SNCF says it expects the high-speed network to return to normal on Monday.  Romain de Calbiac is a French\\u00c2\\u00a0security expert and has told LBC News it was an \\\"extremely well-planned and well-carried out\\\" attack.  \\\"It does demonstrate a level of preparedness and operational expertise that very few actors possess.\\\"  He questioned whether ultra-right or militant environmental groups could be responsible, but also said state-sponsored terrorism should not be ruled out.  \\\"Arson tends to be a preferred modus operandi for Russia operators or Russian-sponsored operators and operating in Europe they have demonstrated that in the past\\\".  Read more:Team GB wins first medal at Paris 2024 Olympics in women's synchronised diving  Read more:Celine Dion kicks off Paris Olympics in rain-drenched opening ceremony after France rocked by rail arson attacks  The use of the Ajax vehicle was halted for two weeks to allow an investigation to be carried out  1h ago  The Home Secretary and Foreign Secretary said they had reached \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009can arrangement\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d with the Chinese government on \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cconsolidating\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Beijing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s diplomatic presence in one site  1h ago  The former 'I am A Celebrity' contestant told followers she was suffering from inflammation all over her body  2h ago  The star told fans he had been dealing with a \\\"lot of health issues over the last year\\\"  3h ago  The Supreme Court ruling said the words \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cwoman\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csex\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d in the Equality Act 2010 refer to a biological woman and biological sex  4h ago  Disney fans confused as to why animation needed different titles across the Atlantic  4h ago  With his side losing 17-7 to the New England Patriots on Monday, Koo lined up a 47-yard field goal attempt, as he had done many times before  4h ago  The use of the Ajax vehicle was halted for two weeks to allow an investigation to be carried out  1h ago  The Home Secretary and Foreign Secretary said they had reached \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009can arrangement\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d with the Chinese government on \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cconsolidating\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Beijing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s diplomatic presence in one site  1h ago  The Supreme Court ruling said the words \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cwoman\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csex\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d in the Equality Act 2010 refer to a biological woman and biological sex  4h ago  The officers made \\\"concerted efforts\\\"  to blame fans in the aftermath  5h ago  A 'quality issue' with metal fuselage panels on multiple\\u00c2\\u00a0A320 models has been discovered.  6h ago  A dozen prisoners have been mistakenly freed in the past month with two remaining at large.  8h ago  Other big name actors such as Dame Judi Dench and Brian Cox are also supporting Age UK's campaign against loneliness.  9h ago  Follow us:  About & Help  Get The LBC App  Legal & Info  Business & Careers  \\u00c2\\u00a9 Global 2025 | 30 Leicester Square, London, WC2H 7LA  Copyright Global 2025. 30 Leicester Square, London. W C 2 H 7 L A.\"}"